subsection:: Aaron Heller diametric decoder

Support for Gerzon's Diametric Decoder Theorem (DDT) footnote::See: E. Benjamin, R. Lee, and A. Heller, "Is My Decoder Ambisonic?," in Proceedings of the 125th Audio Engineering Society Convention, San Francisco, 2008.:: decoding algorithm is derived from Aaron Heller's Octave code available link::http://www.ai.sri.com/ajh/ambisonics/##here::.

Implementation in the SuperCollider3 version of the ATK is by Joseph Anderson.


